The Credence Game
=================

See http://acritch.com/credence-game/ for details.

I (Andrew  M.) added enhancements to the codebase but I lost them a
while ago. Some nursing-related question sets and installation files
which use them are [here](https://www.dropbox.com/sh/12srkai0xgob0pg/AADQe4n8EK44PhjGuj3mjbU0a?dl=0).

